ZH: 如果你不告诉我的话，我就不会知道。
EN: If you don't tell me, I won't know.

ZH: 她的话比较有说服力。
EN: Her words are more persuasive.

ZH: 如果你不放弃的话，你就能成功。
EN: If you don't give up, you will succeed.

ZH: 明天会下雨的话，我们就改变计划。
EN: If it rains tomorrow, we will change our plans.

ZH: 如果你需要任何帮助的话，随时告诉我。
EN: If you need any help, let me know.

ZH: 这个价格太高了，如果能便宜一点的话就好了。
EN: The price is too high, it would be great if it could be cheaper.

ZH: 我会去看演唱会的话，我会通知你。
EN: If I go to the concert, I will let you know.

ZH: 如果你不喜欢这个颜色的话，我可以帮你换一个。
EN: If you don't like this color, I can help you change it.

ZH: 他的话语有点模糊，我不太能理解。
EN: His words are a bit unclear, I can't really understand.

ZH: 如果你迟到的话，会错过演出。
EN: If you are late, you will miss the show.

ZH: 如果你有意见的话，可以提出来。
EN: If you have any opinions, you can speak up.

ZH: 父母的意见很重要，如果他们不同意的话，我们就不能去。
EN: Our parents' opinions are important, if they disagree, we can't go.

ZH: 如果你想预订的话，请提前告诉我。
EN: If you want to make a reservation, please let me know in advance.

ZH: 他今天身体不舒服，如果他出现的话，可能会要求离开。
EN: He is not feeling well today, if he shows up, he might ask to leave.

ZH: 如果你需要帮忙的话，可以找我。
EN: If you need help, you can ask me.

ZH: 我们的飞机延误了，如果不能赶上的话，得改变行程。
EN: Our flight is delayed, if we can't make it, we will have to change our itinerary.

ZH: 我在公司会议上发言，如果你想听的话，可以一起来。
EN: I will be speaking at the company meeting, if you want to listen, you can come along.

ZH: 如果你要加班的话，我可以帮你处理别的事情。
EN: If you need to work overtime, I can help you with other tasks.

ZH: 如果我们迟到的话，就会错过开场。
EN: If we are late, we will miss the beginning.

ZH: 你的建议很有帮助，如果你有更多的话，请告诉我。
EN: Your suggestions are very helpful, if you have more, please let me know.
